%80-%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDvs-code%E5%B9%B6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 一、官网下载VS Code并安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C-%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDmingw%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 二、下载MinGW编译器</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 三、安装编译器</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9%E5%8C%85%E5%85%88%E5%B0%86%E9%87%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8B%96%E5%88%B0%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8A\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 1.打开压缩包，先将里面的文件拖到桌面上</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E5%B0%86%E5%88%9A%E5%88%9A%E6%8B%BF%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84mingw64%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%88%B0cprogram-files%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 2.将刚刚拿出来的mingw64文件夹，移动到C:\\Program Files目录下</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E9%9A%8F%E4%BE%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%82%B9%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E5%90%8E%E9%9D%A2%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEvscode%E4%BC%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 3.现在随便用点什么东西，记下下面三个路径（后面配置vscode会用到）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%BE%E6%89%80%E7%A4%BA%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 4.按下图所示步骤打开【高级系统设置】</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 5.打开环境变量配置窗口</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\